text: Francesca Hayward (born July 1992) is an English ballet dancer and actress. She is a main dancer in the Royal Ballet at Covent Garden in London. In 2019, she starred as Victoria the White Cat in the musical movie Cats, a movie version of the stage musical of the same name.
